<div id="review_1926967183" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1926967183" />
    <a title="Raneta" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10556177-raneta"><img alt="Raneta" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1340914120p2/10556177.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1926967183?book_show_action=true">Mar 11, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Raneta" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Raneta" href="/user/show/10556177-raneta">Raneta</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1926967183" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14249665257974918581">It took me a while to adapt to the poetry and prose mixture, but it was well worth it. The way the poetry is interspersed with prose makes the book both visually and mentally lyrical. As a result, the story is much more compelling than it otherwise might have been. Indeed, after reading it, I realized that this short book about journeys and discoveries couldn&apos;t have been told any other way. Look forward to reading more from this author.</span>
  <span id="freeText14249665257974918581" style="display:none">It took me a while to adapt to the poetry and prose mixture, but it was well worth it. The way the poetry is interspersed with prose makes the book both visually and mentally lyrical. As a result, the story is much more compelling than it otherwise might have been. Indeed, after reading it, I realized that this short book about journeys and discoveries couldn't have been told any other way. Look forward to reading more from this author.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14249665257974918581" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
